@node "INTRO" "Introduction"
@next "IMPORTANT"
@prev "Main"

 =========================================================================
                           INTRODUCTION
 =========================================================================


        PREFACE

	MessagePlus is an AREXX proggy allowing you to use US Robotics 
	Message Plus modem (ONLY !!) as answering machine. MessagePlus 
	modem can handle incoming voice and Fax messages even if the 
	connected computer is switched OFF.

	I programmed this little script to dialog with the 2 Mo modem 
	memory easily. All you have to do is to configure the modem to
	your needs and save the settings !
	
	MessagePlus uses between 0 to 1% Cpu time.
	
	IMPORTANT 
	
	There is some essential things to know otherwise your modem won't
	work correctly. These MUST KNOW things are explained in the
        @{"IMPORTANT NOTES" link "IMPORTANT" 0}.
        
        This proggy is postcardware, so PLEASE, HELP ME to fill my fridge, 
        bedroom, ... with postcards from all over the world !!!
        
        If you like MessagePlus and would like improve it, you're welcome
        in the development team. See @{"Author" link "AUTHOR" 0} for more information.

 	I won't release any other version until I receive 100 postcards. 
 	
  =========================================================================
@endnode

@node "IMPORTANT" "Important notes"
@next "REQUIREMENTS"
@prev "INTRO"

 =========================================================================
                      	 IMPORTANT NOTES
 =========================================================================


	BE ADVICED :
	------------

	The modem will NOT handle incoming calls if the ARQ/FAX LED is RED.
	See @{"USAGE" link "USAGE" 0} for more details.

	-> Always check for a GREEN Led before leaving modem answering.

	Message Plus modems have an INTERNAL clock. To function correctly
	this CLOCK MUST BE REINITIALIZED oftenly and at least EACH TIME
	THE MODEM IS SWITCHED OFF. 
	
	-> THE SCRIPT WILL AUTOMATICALY RESET CLOCK AT START UP IF NEEDED. 
	Perform a RESET CLOCK every time the modem act strangely. Note in
	this case, that messages date/time displayed will be affected.

	To guess the time a message was left, this script need to store
	the last clock reset time. In order to be as independant as
	possible, this program will save the current Date and time
	in the modem's 4th PHONE NUMBER MEMORY. 

	-> NEVER store any number in this 4th memory otherwise the time 
	stamps will be totally silly !!

	A new flash rom is available on USR website www.3com.com. DOWNLOAD
	IT, to get compatible with the new V90 57600 bauds standart.
	You will also have the possiblity to hear messages without Amiga
	by pressing the volume button. 
	Check USR website for more informations.

	Special notes/distibute conditions:
	-----------------------------------

        DISCLAIMER

        You use this libraries and the programs in the archive entirely at
        your own risk. I'm not responsible for any damage on your
        software nor your hardware. You should read the documentation
        confirmly before you use any @{"functions" link "USAGE" 0} in this application.

	DISTRIBUTION

	This archive is distributed as POSTCARDWARE on these conditions:

