	  containing the package) to me (contact for address details).
	- Amiga resellers that includes this package with Message Plus
	  modems MUST contact @{"me" link "AUTHOR" 0}.

	Aminet, Fred Fish, Meeting Pearls and BBS'es are allowed to
	distribute this archive freely.

	BUGS

	There are bugs in every software. I can't guarantee that this
	software is bugfree, but I will try to make it as bugfree as
	possible. To do so @{"I need your help" link "AUTHOR" 0}. If you discover strange
	behaviour or bugs please contact me and describe what you did to
	get the behaviour or the bug appearance.


