 =========================================================================
                  	 FUTURE ENHANCEMENTS
 =========================================================================



	Messplus is far much complete than any other sofware for any 
	platform concerning the modem answering machine control.
	
	In this first version the message download to computer isn't 
	implemented. So, faxs can be received but not viewed :-(
	
	This proggy (fully fonctionnal) is PostcardWare. I won't release
 	any other version before receiving 100 postcards. 

	Languages already supported are English and French. If you want
	to write a catalog, you MUST respect the exact rules : sentences
	with quotes and / commands. Otherwise the script won't be able
	to interpret them correctly. Feel free to ask me for any problem
	and send me your work, I'll be happy to distribute it with next
	versions and include you in development team and credits... 
	
	Before working on future enhancements, I prefer waiting for all
	users requests. So feel free to send @{"me" link "AUTHOR" 0} your ideas and bug
	reports. Note, that I'll probably work on your own request faster 
	if I receive your own Postcard... ;-)

        No distribution of programs based on my scripts are allowed without
        permission.
	
 	To other modem users : you're free to use or modify this GUI 
 	to send your modem specific Voice commands. Try to get the
 	Technical reference for your modem and modify the MCOMMAND lines.
 	Please tell me about your work, I'll tell you if anybody is also
 	working on the same subject.

	An special Olitec modems version is studied. Mail me for more
	information.

 =========================================================================
@endnode

